High-Quality Felt Cloth: Made from durable felt cloth, this storage bag offers a stylish yet practical solution for car organization. The felt material is both sturdy and water-resistant, making it ideal for withstanding spills and everyday wear and tear.

Lightweight and Durable: Weighing just 160g, this car seat back storage bag is lightweight yet durable.
